{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839724846,"sessionID":"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u","part":{"id":"prt_d784b379c001VJF5sWEIwRmf96","messageID":"msg_d784b18cb0019nqZuLWh6SC9xe","sessionID":"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_644a537bdf044ea0beb35c11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-002/README.md","content":"# AR-002 â€” CRD CodeInterpreter ç±»ĺž‹ĺ®šäą‰\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n## Summary\n\nDefine the CRD (Custom Resource Definition) types for CodeInterpreter in the pkg/apis module.\n\n## Status\n\n- [ ] Scaffold directory structure\n- [ ] Define CodeInterpreter CRD types\n- [ ] Add Go type definitions\n- [ ] Generate CRD manifests\n- [ ] Add unit tests\n\n## Notes\n\nSee `notes/` directory for implementation notes and decisions.\n\n## Source Files\n\nSee `src/` directory for source code changes.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-002/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-002/README.md","time":{"start":1775839724818,"end":1775839724845}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839724848,"sessionID":"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u","part":{"id":"prt_d784b532c001pg0Ys22xGR7L5g","messageID":"msg_d784b18cb0019nqZuLWh6SC9xe","sessionID":"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_a7e19d9c79ff4125b0e0e93f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-002 â€” CRD CodeInterpreter ç±»ĺž‹ĺ®šäą‰ Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Scaffold & Registration\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/` directory structure\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/register.go` - register API group\n- [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/register.go` - define `SchemeGroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Type Definitions\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Define `CodeInterpreterPhase` enum (Pending, Running, Failed, Terminating)\n- [ ] **2.2** Define `CodeInterpreterCondition` struct (type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime)\n- [ ] **2.3** Define `KernelSpec` struct (language, image, resources)\n- [ ] **2.4** Define `SessionConfig` struct (timeout, idleTimeout, maxSessions)\n- [ ] **2.5** Define `SecurityPolicy` struct (allowedPackages, blockedOperations, networkAccess)\n- [ ] **2.6** Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct (kernel, session, security, resources)\n- [ ] **2.7** Define `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct (phase, conditions, activeSessions, startTime, lastTransitionTime)\n- [ ] **2.8** Define `CodeInterpreter` struct (TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, Status)\n- [ ] **2.9** Define `CodeInterpreterList` struct (TypeMeta, ListMeta, Items)\n- [ ] **2.10** Add JSON tags (camelCase) and protobuf tags to all types\n- [ ] **2.11** Implement `runtime.Object` interface for CodeInterpreter and CodeInterpreterList\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Defaults & Validation\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/defaults.go`\n- [ ] **3.2** Implement `SetDefaults_CodeInterpreter` - set default phase to Pending, default kernel settings\n- [ ] **3.3** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/validation.go`\n- [ ] **3.4** Implement `ValidateCodeInterpreter` - validate spec fields (kernel language, resource values, security policies)\n- [ ] **3.5** Implement `ValidateCodeInterpreterStatusUpdate` - validate status transitions and field immutability\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: CRD Manifest Generation\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Add `+genclient` and `+k8s:deepcopy-gen` markers to type definitions\n- [ ] **4.2** Add `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` and `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` markers\n- [ ] **4.3** Add `+kubebuilder:printcolumn` markers for kubectl output (NAME, PHASE, KERNEL, AGE)\n- [ ] **4.4** Run `make gen-crd` (controller-gen) to generate CRD YAML\n- [ ] **4.5** Verify generated manifest at `manifests/charts/base/crds/codeinterpreter.yaml`\n- [ ] **4.6** Validate OpenAPI v3 schema in generated CRD\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Client Code Generation\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Update `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` if needed\n- [ ] **5.2** Update `hack/update-codegen.sh` with API group info\n- [ ] **5.3** Run `make gen-client` to generate clientset, listers, informers\n- [ ] **5.4** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/clientset/versioned/`\n- [ ] **5.5** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/listers/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/`\n- [ ] **5.6** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/informers/externalversions/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n- [ ] **6.2** Test type round-trip serialization (Go â†’ JSON â†’ Go)\n- [ ] **6.3** Test `SetDefaults_CodeInterpreter` behavior\n- [ ] **6.4** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/validation_test.go`\n- [ ] **6.5** Test valid CodeInterpreter specs pass validation\n- [ ] **6.6** Test invalid specs fail validation (unsupported languages, negative resources)\n- [ ] **6.7** Test status update validation (phase transitions, immutable fields)\n- [ ] **6.8** Test `AddToScheme` registration works correctly\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Integration & Verification\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Run `make test` - all unit tests pass\n- [ ] **7.2** Run `make verify` - code generation is up to date\n- [ ] **7.3** Apply CRD to test cluster: `kubectl apply -f manifests/charts/base/crds/codeinterpreter.yaml`\n- [ ] **7.4** Verify `kubectl get codeinterpreter` shows custom columns\n- [ ] **7.5** Create sample CodeInterpreter YAML in `examples/codeinterpreter.yaml`\n- [ ] **7.6** Apply sample and verify resource is created\n- [ ] **7.7** Verify Go client can create/get/update CodeInterpreter resources\n\n---\n\n## Verification Checklist\n\n- [ ] All Go code compiles without errors\n- [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/...` passes with â‰Ą80% coverage\n- [ ] CRD manifest validates with `kubeval` or `kubectl --dry-run=server`\n- [ ] Generated client code is up to date (`git diff` shows no changes after `make gen-client`)\n- [ ] Example YAML applies successfully to test cluster\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| Phase 2 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 3 | Phase 2 |\n| Phase 4 | Phase 2 |\n| Phase 5 | Phase 4 |\n| Phase 6 | Phase 2, 3 |\n| Phase 7 | Phase 4, 5, 6 |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-002/proposal.md`\n- Implementation Plan: `proposal.md#implementation-plan`\n- Success Criteria: `proposal.md#success-criteria`\n- API Conventions: `https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md`\n- Related: `changes/AR-001/` (AgentRuntime CRD)\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_